snippet.textDisplay:
Thank you Coke Studio. Everytime i hear your music, it's as though I am in the presence of the unseen divine in this world and beyond. Thank you for reminding us that when life hits you with its hardest challenges, take it in your stride, just jhoom, and go out there and live your best life. I eagerly wait for the rest of the songs of this season! Best wishes from Singapore!

PS: i hope your songs will have english translations too, it helps me learn the meaning of thee lyrics in urdu/whatever language is used in the song :)
